OL,3,CClub 'appalled and disgusted' at
OL,4,Cdamage caused to fire memorial
OL,6,FBradford City Football Club says it is
OL,7,Fappalled and disgusted at damage
OL,8,Fcaused to the Valley Parade Fire
OL,9,FMemorial earlier this week.
OL,11,FOn 11 May 1985, 56 football fans lost
OL,12,Ftheir lives when the Valley Parade
OL,13,Fmain stand caught fire at the Batams
OL,14,Flast game of the season against
OL,15,FLincoln City. Hundreds more were left
OL,16,Fwith life-changing injuries.
OL,18,FThe club says the memorial, which was
OL,19,Finstalled in 2001, has since repaired.
