OL,3,CClub 'appalled and disgusted' at
OL,4,Cdamage caused to fire memorial
OL,6,FIn a statement, the club said: "To say
OL,7,Fthis act is wholly unacceptable does
OL,8,Fnot go far enough - it is utterly
OL,9,Fincomprehensible.
OL,11,F"This memorial is sacred to our club,
OL,12,Four supporters, and the people of
OL,13,FBradford.
OL,15,F"It is a place of remembrance and
OL,16,Freflection, honouring the 56 Bradford
OL,17,FCity and Lincoln City supporters who
OL,18,Flost their lives in the Valley Parade
OL,19,FFire Disaster, and the hundreds more
OL,20,Fwho were left with life-changing
OL,21,Finjuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
