OL,3,CClub 'appalled and disgusted' at
OL,4,Cdamage caused to fire memorial
OL,6,F"The memorial has been tended to daily
OL,7,Fby our staff, who clean and maintain
OL,8,Fit with the utmost care and respect.
OL,10,F"While the damage has since been
OL,11,Frepaired, the pain this has caused
OL,12,Fcannot simply be undone. We stand
OL,13,Ftogether as a club and as a city in
OL,14,Fcondemning this shameful act.
OL,16,F"Bradford City AFC will not tolerate
OL,17,Fsuch disrespect."
