OL,3,CClub 'appalled and disgusted' at
OL,4,Cdamage caused to fire memorial
OL,6,FThe club says it is reviewing CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage from around the ground and is
OL,8,Fworking closely with authorities to
OL,9,Fidentify those responsibly.
OL,11,FIt's also urging anyone with
OL,12,Finformation to come forward.
OL,14,FIn January four Carlisle United fans
OL,15,Fwere arrested after reports of tragedy
OL,16,Fchanting during their match against
OL,17,FBradford City.
OL,19,FThe reported chants are believed to be
OL,20,Frelated to the Valley Parade fire
OL,21,Fdisaster.
